another dimension.

00:41:21.590 --> 00:41:26.630
I think that kind of rigor is
more helpful than a sort of a

00:41:26.630 --> 00:41:29.530
general permissiveness
about creativity.

00:41:29.530 --> 00:41:33.820
So that's my answer, is I
would say, you should be

00:41:33.820 --> 00:41:37.960
disruptive and you should zag
when other people are zigging.

00:41:37.960 --> 00:41:40.600
And that doesn't
mean, therefore

00:41:40.600 --> 00:41:42.310
let's just be creative.

00:41:42.310 --> 00:41:42.850
Is that a?

